      • findAllTransactionalAccountsPerClientId

        @Query(value="SELECT ca.client_id, c.surname ,ca.client_account_number,t.description, ca.display_balance FROM client_account ca  join client c on c.client_id = ca.client_id join account_type t on ca.account_type_code =  t.account_type_code WHERE (ca.client_id,ca.display_balance) IN  (SELECT c.client_id, MAX(c.display_balance)  FROM client_account c  join account_type t on c.account_type_code =  t.account_type_code  where t.transactional = true  GROUP BY c.client_id)  order by ca.display_balance desc",
       nativeQuery=true)
